Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.62,0:00:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hanasaku Iroha
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:19.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.37,0:00:23.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not actually your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:27.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend, an ailing jazz singer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:31.15,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,had a child with an American \Nsoldier who arrived at port.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.91,0:00:35.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I don't \Nhave female friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:38.43,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Secondly, that's not something a \Nchild confesses to their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Was worth a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:46.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Little miss Ohana, do you know \Nhow babies are made?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:51.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the stork theory over \Nthe cabbage patch theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:52.52,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.70,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Digging up babies from a cabbage \Npatch sounds quite deranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, a deadline reminder call!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:00:59.12,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Quick! Get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:00.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:02.27,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:04.36,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But my hands are wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Matsumae residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.88,0:01:07.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:08.08,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.52,0:01:08.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:12.44,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:13.95,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.95,0:01:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The editors are being so mean to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.72,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming over tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.97,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What? If we need to talk, \Nlet's do it over a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:22.93,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,There will be dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.95,0:01:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Episode 1: It's Spring,\NI'm 16, and I'm Still a Bud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.38,0:01:24.47,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Made by Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko, I've got a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.52,0:01:33.37,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,How do you eat the corn kernels in canned soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:39.59,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,They always get stuck to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:43.41,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You look so ridiculous right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can'h geh 'em ouh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:48.42,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just pour some water in the can?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.89,0:01:52.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That would ruin the taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The corn's as good as gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.53,0:01:59.99,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could dump the \Nwater into another cup,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and just eat the corn with chopsticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.38,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Here I thought your plan \Nwas lazy and crude,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's actually quite \Npatient and elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:09.04,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Hush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:17.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko's so patient! Ko's so patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.27,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Have you chosen your junior year electives yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.11,0:02:22.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.17,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,What career will you pursue after graduation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:29.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna decide yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:32.20,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,You really play everything \Nby ear, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.48,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that up, and you'll ruin yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,"Ruin myself," huh? I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.00,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What boring scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.58,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A mere fraction of sky is visible;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the rest blocked by tall buildings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A transient escape on a packed train,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the sunset dyes the city vermillion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.25,0:02:57.75,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that sounds pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:03.65,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I may not act like it, but I'm \Nactually pretty pragmatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:06.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't live with the greatest role model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.41,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, your mom is quite the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:12.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if I don't decide \Non what to do right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.23,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll end up finding a stable job,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.23,0:03:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,getting married around age 26,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,then buying a plot at the cemetery \Nin block 3 once I get old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:23.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me gravestones there can be pretty pricey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,If you can afford one, you should be fine—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:30.99,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You lose! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:31.82,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:34.96,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Got any plans for spring break?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:41.31,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I do like this time of day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Lights flicker on, one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:08.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,illuminating my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:11.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they also light the way to my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And I hope that, at \Nthe end of that path,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have changed for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.64,0:04:24.32,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.03,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Great! You're finally home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.50,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.11,0:04:31.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,He's fallen into debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:35.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So you're doing a moonlight flit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.17,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see, he gave them our address!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.59,Default,BF,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:43.87,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,And when are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.74,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.36,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Strike while the iron's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.24,Default,BF,0000,0000,0000,,Though there's nothing hot about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.24,0:04:49.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:52.60,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,This is all your fault, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm living in a soap opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a nosebleed coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.37,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That sensitive nose of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:04.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe this is a chance\Nfor me to reinvent myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.83,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,So, are we fleeing north or south?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:09.58,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.08,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:13.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if we're going somewhere cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need to buy some more warm clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.91,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But if we're going somewhere warm, \Nthen maybe I should get a sundress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:24.05,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of parent runs \Naway with their kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:28.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of parent runs \Naway {\i1}without{\i0} their kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.80,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kissuisou
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:36.42,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.42,0:05:37.33,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:38.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:42.96,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:47.43,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm going to my grandma's by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.72,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be going to school there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:51.25,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:53.24,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.80,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look so pessimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.25,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of face is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.78,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Since Grandma and Mom are on bad terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know a single thing about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.95,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't living in a hot spring inn sound dramatic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:13.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Though, personally, I think a moonlight flit would've been more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:15.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:20.77,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the kind of guy who reaches the \Ncorn by flooding it with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.48,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that was pretty original.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:28.33,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I do things in a roundabout way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:31.28,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,So as your best friend, I figured someday you'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.31,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see now that I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:40.22,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I thought if we were always together, \Nyou'd figure out how I feel about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.11,0:06:43.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ko, could you be a bit clearer—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:47.06,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it now: I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:47.51,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:50.55,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,I've always liked you, Ohana Matsumae!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.31,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:02.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, you like me? What does that—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:07.01,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:07.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.05,Default,Ko,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:10.57,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, Ko—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:19.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He left before I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The scenery outside reflects \Nthe feelings in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:34.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected anything \Nfrom Mom in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and I've always wanted to \Nbe someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:42.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But after seeing a \Ndifferent side of Ko...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:51.17,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't come to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.74,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Care for a piece of candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.66,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:08:02.53,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to meet an \Nelderly woman who gives out candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.62,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,This is so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.37,0:08:16.68,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:20.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such a vast ocean before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.76,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:24.44,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,With the way I was feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually content \Nbeing in the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:31.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But now that we're out, \NI can't help feeling excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Kissuisou
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.77,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What a grand stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.69,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm in a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.46,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Weeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:40.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're ruining the image of my fairy-tale perfect hot spring inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:52.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it really was a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:57.74,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,A pretty girl reached out \Nher hand to me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:58.91,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,...told me to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.56,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, you surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Could you repeat that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:14.92,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You can't go around wishing death \Non a complete stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.19,0:10:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are actually wild rocamboles \NMinchi's been growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Rocamboles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:32.52,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.90,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They're edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:36.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Rocampoes? Minchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:37.57,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Rocam{\i1}boles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.79,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Minchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:41.91,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Ohana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:52.84,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.96,0:10:54.84,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:11:00.47,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Another elderly lady who hands out candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:01.30,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:05.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hanasaku Iroha
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:16.97,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.56,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, you are an employee of this establishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.12,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,An employee?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:23.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Not your granddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.19,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You're the daughter of \Nthe girl I disowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worth cats and dogs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.62,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You'll earn your keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Are you training me to \Nbecome the next manager—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.07,0:11:36.36,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Nwah, I'm having you take \Ncare of random chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.36,0:11:37.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Nwah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.88,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You can do whatever you want \Nafter you graduate high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:41.69,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You will be paid for your work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.43,0:11:43.58,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:45.80,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.80,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Any blunders will be docked from your wages.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.80,0:11:50.08,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful I'm feeding you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and putting a roof over your head, in this day and age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.41,0:12:00.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a grandmother who \Nhands out candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll be here soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:04.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:05.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you must be Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:23.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nice to meet—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.97,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind getting off me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops, my apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The more I look at you, the more I see the resemblance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:36.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Those evil eyes always scheming \Nways to screw me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:40.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Those sharp canines always looking \Nto leave bite marks in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:44.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um, are you my mom's brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:48.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I may use you to work \Noff my long-standing grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:55.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, just teasin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.59,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so you're Ohana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.93,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:07.05,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I have a million questions for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:09.61,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,What's Satsuki like?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.00,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard she's quite the call girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she walk around \Nthe house naked, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:15.06,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.95,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'm Tomoe, the head waitress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.95,0:13:19.65,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Your superior, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.18,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you anything \Nyou want to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.18,0:13:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll need to share info in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.16,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.00,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.41,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,She's apparently a \Nmanagement consultant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:36.46,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Our Enishi just can't \Nsay no to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sloppy coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:40.07,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Is Satsuki like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:41.75,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Sloppy from the waist down, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:43.34,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:45.91,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's beanman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in charge of building maintenance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.18,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Is he nicknamed that \Nbecause he's small?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.25,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,No, he shares his last name, Denroku, \Nwith a company that sells beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:57.19,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tohru, the assistant chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.19,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,And the one back there's \Nthe head cook, Mr. Ren.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:02.27,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,He has a crew cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.81,0:14:06.60,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,They looked busy, so I'll \Nintroduce you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.37,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I forgetting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.00,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're sixteen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:12.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.15,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:16.13,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.24,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Great timing, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.63,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The girl who told me to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.88,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you've already met?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.88,0:14:23.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No, not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:24.88,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.98,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, that saves time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:28.51,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Their names are Minko and Nako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.39,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're all the same age,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you mind giving her a quick tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.37,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:35.89,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.77,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Nako.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:42.66,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:48.75,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She obviously doesn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:55.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I was sort of expecting an, \N"of course she does!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.82,0:15:02.16,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's the high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.51,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Minchi and I go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you two work here part-time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.51,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I do. Minchi lives here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.88,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, there was a school \Nuniform hanging in my room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're roommates!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:17.30,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.04,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that uniform was really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:21.98,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.90,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The colors were certainly unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.42,Default,Nako,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.69,0:15:33.05,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Should we head back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:44.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't exactly \Nwhat I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:51.02,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I wasn't even sure what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:53.77,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,You dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.35,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you peel the skin so thick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:57.85,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:16:01.30,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Ever considered what the farmers \Nwho grew these went through?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.06,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:05.12,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,And what about your poor grandmother,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.12,0:16:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who make dishes out of the skins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.96,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,My grandmother doesn't live with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:11.67,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Just use your imagination, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.36,0:16:13.24,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.24,0:16:14.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:20.70,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you the manager's \Ngranddaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're being too hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.33,0:16:26.70,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yelling at someone doesn't \Nhelp them improve, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:28.04,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Y—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:29.17,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.55,0:16:33.57,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:35.69,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Do a little more working, \Nand a little less talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:36.57,Default,Minchi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.83,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you mind letting \Nus do our thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:43.91,Default,Tohru,0000,0000,0000,,We have our own rules here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.03,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Man, am I beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.20,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,My life's taken a turn for the weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.01,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I've got \Nnowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:07.41,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.13,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Ko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}From: Satsuki\NGood luck, Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.98,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.55,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You make it sound so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:29.86,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,It's a bit awkward for \Nme to contact Ko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.11,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,The drama I'd been longing for so badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned out to be kind of \Nlonely and moldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:49.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,M-My back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.37,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,She went to sleep after I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and got up earlier than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:16.28,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way someone can sleep \Nwell on such a moldy bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.45,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,There... we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.39,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,New here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.67,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.49,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.05,0:18:43.26,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.02,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:47.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Please, it's all right. \NYou don't need to bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:48.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:52.01,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Right! It was just a falling futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.01,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Ohana!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.89,0:18:56.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really sorry. I didn't notice—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.36,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,"My sincerest apologies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.07,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,M-My sincerest apolo–gies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No one was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.52,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.32,0:19:14.25,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.27,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe, summon Minko as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:17.76,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.92,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Minko's futon was really squashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.92,0:19:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I wanted to hang it outside for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.30,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,At the front of the inn, \Nwhere our customers enter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.64,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There wasn't much light in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted to hang it out in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.75,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,At an inn, customers always come first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:37.70,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,You come last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.09,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.84,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Even {\i1}after{\i0} that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.22,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I agree that customers are important,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:52.79,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,but I also think it's important to \Nreward people who work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.79,Default,Tomoe,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:57.92,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, Minko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.11,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:13.70,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,This girl inconvenienced a customer while \Ntrying to hang {\i1}your{\i0} futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:17.34,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you old enough to take care of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:18.53,Default,Minko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:20.19,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,G-Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.45,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Do not call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.30,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Manager, I'm the one at fault here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.30,0:20:25.42,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,You're being unreasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.55,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,How would it look if I slapped \Na customer like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:31.41,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Far worse than "unreasonable," \Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.03,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,And you did just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.66,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,Life here revolves around our customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:42.40,Default,Grand,0000,0000,0000,,This is a basic principle. If you can't\Naccept that, you shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.62,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.54,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.21,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that someone who \Nworks so hard was slapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.98,0:20:55.73,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,and customers were inconvenienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:58.61,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,all because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:17.33,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.14,Default,Ohana,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm really sorry!
